headline: PIZZA HUT® CREATES A FIRST-OF-ITS-KIND INNOVATION: "PIZZA CAVIAR"
summary: Pizza Hut is putting an indulgent twist on the caviar craze sweeping foodie culture with the launch of "Pizza Caviar"* – a first-of-its-kind innovation that transforms the fine dining trend into something completely unexpected. Caviar has been elevating some of the world's most beloved comfort foods with the unexpected hi-low pairings popping up in upscale restaurants and gracing social feeds across the country.
